title: Pack up and leave, PKR Youth tells North Korea
text:
More PKR Youth wants the North Korean embassy in Kuala Lumpur to "pack up and leave" following its remarks against the Malaysian police. The party's national deputy youth chief Afif Bahardin also urged the federal government and Wisma Putra to shut down the Malaysian consulate in North Korea. "North Korea's remarks are rude, overboard and an insult to the police and country's sovereignty.
